---
---

<section class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center px-6 md:px-10 pt-28 pb-20 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Dot-matrix Creation of Adam hands -->
  <canvas id="adam-hands-canvas" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full pointer-events-none hidden md:block opacity-60"></canvas>

  <!-- Content (above canvas) -->
  <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center">
    <!-- Badge -->
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-bg-card/60 border border-border px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs text-text-secondary mb-8 backdrop-blur-sm animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
      <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-green-500 rounded-full animate-pulse-dot"></span>
      Disponível para novos projetos
    </div>

    <!-- Heading -->
    <h1 class="text-[40px] md:text-[72px] font-extrabold leading-[1.02] tracking-[-3px] max-w-[900px] mb-6 animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
      Sua ideia merece<br>
      <span class="gradient-text">virar realidade</span>
    </h1>

    <!-- Subheading -->
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-text-secondary max-w-[520px] leading-relaxed mb-10 animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.6s;">
      Você tem a visão. Nós temos a expertise para transformá-la em um produto digital de verdade — do zero ao lançamento.
    </p>

    <!-- CTAs -->
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mb-16 animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.8s;">
      <a href="#contato" class="btn-primary">Quero Meu Projeto →</a>
      <a href="#resultados" class="btn-secondary">Veja Resultados ↓</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats -->
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-8 sm:gap-12 pt-10 border-t border-border animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 1s;">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-accent tracking-tight" data-target="50">0+</div>
        <div class="text-xs text-text-muted uppercase tracking-wider mt-1">Projetos Entregues</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-accent tracking-tight" data-target="5">0+</div>
        <div class="text-xs text-text-muted uppercase tracking-wider mt-1">Anos de Experiência</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-accent tracking-tight" data-target="100">0%</div>
        <div class="text-xs text-text-muted uppercase tracking-wider mt-1">Satisfação</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
